* {{monsymlink|rabbit}}
* {{yellow|r}} [[hedgehog]]
* {{monsymlink|black rat}}
* {{monsymlink|pack rat}}
* {{monsymlink|hellrat}}
* {{monsymlink|enormous rat|variant=UnNetHack}}
